499
00:21:50,458 --> 00:21:52,875
- If you rely on your sister
for guidance

500
00:21:52,958 --> 00:21:56,000
even when she's still so young,
you'll never find your answer.

501
00:21:56,083 --> 00:21:58,291
- Listen, I know
it might seem pathetic,

502
00:21:58,375 --> 00:22:00,916
but you're the only one
I can count on.

503
00:22:01,958 --> 00:22:02,875
So, please...

504
00:22:02,958 --> 00:22:04,041
- Now tell me.

505
00:22:04,125 --> 00:22:05,875
